Package: artcdn
Title: CDN Storage Operations for DigitalOcean Spaces
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Bobby", "Fatemi", , "bobby@artalytics.app", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Centralized CDN storage operations for DigitalOcean Spaces buckets.
    Provides a registry-driven bucket configuration, cached S3 client, and generic
    primitives for uploading, listing, checking, and deleting objects. Designed as the
    single storage layer for both platform and agent infrastructure workloads.
